        <bioghist id="ref5">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Timothy Pickering was a soldier, Indian agent, and Secretary of War. He was elected to the American Philosophical Society in 1795.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <originalsloc id="ref3">
            <head>Existence and Location of Originals note</head>
